  section#header
    div.section-summary
      h1 Engineering Excellence,
       br
       span.brand Delivered
      p.large Radian Advisory provides comprehensive engineering consulting services to help your business solve complex technical challenges and drive innovation forward.
      a(href="#contact").button Contact Us

  section#approach
    div.section-summary
      h2 Our Approach
      p.large With decades of combined experience in engineering and technology, we bring deep expertise and innovative solutions to every project.
    div.section-columns
      div.section-left-column
        //- h3 Our Expertise
        //- p.large We specialize in providing strategic engineering consulting across multiple disciplines, helping organizations navigate complex technical challenges and implement cutting-edge solutions.
        //- p.large Our team combines technical excellence with business acumen to deliver results that drive real value for our clients.
        div.team-photo
          img(src="/static/team.webp" alt="A photo of the Radian Advisory team at a construction site giving a thumbs up")
        div.banner
          div.icon
            svg(xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true")
