          p Based in Brisbane, Australia
      div.section-right-column
        div.card
          h3.brand-line Innovation-Driven
          p We stay at the forefront of technological advancement to bring you the most innovative solutions.
        div.card
          h3.brand-line Client-Focused
          p Every solution is tailored to your specific needs and business objectives.
        div.card
          h3.brand-line Results-Oriented
          p We measure success by the tangible impact we create for your organization.

